3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new network module that collects effective spatial features and embeds location information, which are common techniques in machine learning. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper deals with the problem of understanding the relationships between objects in an image, which can be seen as a language understanding task. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper proposes a new network module that improves the performance of an existing network by utilizing broadcasting and multiwise relations, which are techniques commonly used in neural networks.
